data.description: CAPE COD STYLE HOME WITH MASTER ON MAIN, 2 BDRMS UPSTAIRS, 4TH BDRM IN THE FINISHED BASEMENT. EAT-IN KITCHEN WITH A BUILT-IN SHELVING SYSTEM. SEP LR W/GAS FIREPLACE. MASTER BATH HAS DOUBLE VANITY, SEPARATE SHOWER, AND OVERSIZED GARDEN TUB. UPSTAIRS BDRMS ARE LARGE AND ROOMY. THE BASEMENT HAS A FINISHED ROOM PERFECT FOR A DEN WITH TILED FLOORING. THE SEMI-WRAP-AROUND FRONT PORCH IS SPACIOUS AND PERFECT FOR WARM, SUMMER EVENINGS. SHED IN BACK FOR EXTRA STORAGE. THE BACK DECK OVERLOOKS SERENE WOODS WITH A BEAUTIFUL FLOWING CREEK WITH A SMALL BRIDGE. LARGE LOT CLOSE TO AN ACRE (0.82). GREAT LOCATION CLOSE TO SHOPPING, INTERSTATE, AND SCHOOLS. LV FLOORING ON THE MAIN AND CARPET UPSTAIRS. STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES IN THE KITCHEN. FLOORS, KITCHEN COUNTERTOPS, AND RETAINING WALL WERE UPDATED IN 2019. NEW ROOF AND WATER HEATER INSTALLED MARCH OF 2023.
